Ember-testing / QUnit / jquery-mockjax

To run the javascript tests

    npm install
    export PATH="./node_modules/.bin:$PATH"
    bower install
    karma start


To run the ember.js web app

    npm install
    export PATH="./node_modules/.bin:$PATH"
    bower install

    ./bin/server
    http://localhost:3000

Known issues: does not yet work with RC6

https://github.com/emberjs/ember.js/pull/3026
